entries.femaleVariant: What'd I tell ya? That's her! Blue Moon!
Uh, hey, sorry! Could I get a picture with you? I'm a huge fan...
What're you doing here?
What're you doing here?
Yeah, yeah... Perfect...
Her again? For fuck's sakes...
Bullshit. She's way too fat.
<mothertongue l="jpn" m="kuzu-yarou" b="Speak for yourself, " a=""/>
Oh-hahahaha! In yo FACE!
I know!
Hey! "Pillow Fight's" an amazing song!
Sure. What's your name?
Green Cloud!
<mothertongue l="jpn" m="San... Ni... Ichi... Chi-zu!" b="Haha! Awesome! " a=" There we go!"/>
Admiring the view until you showed up.
So you think I'm a kid, huh?! I gave you everything! Everything!!
I... I don't even know who you are! V! V, help!
Hey, isn't... Fuck, it is her!
So fuckin' bored. Gimme a hit.
"Gimme," he says. Gimme the eddies, first.
A drink, hehe... that's what I need... just a liiiitle sip...
Ugh... my lips! They're burnin'! Hot, hot, hot...!
Mh, fuck! She's incredible!
United in life... united in death!
Shit! Bitch point-blank shot her, yo!
Fuck's goin' on over here?!
You're here... awesome. So listen up, in a second I'm gonna get up and walk a little, OK?
Fweet, fweet... What's a girl like you doing around here?
Lookin' to get lucky, eh?
Mhm. You're lucky if I don't rip your eyes out. Any takers? No? Then shut your yaps.
Bleh. Crusty, old geezers.
Change the fuckin' track, will ya?
Watch out for those gangoons, Blue Moon...
Careful. Those guys look like trouble.
Eh, just your neighborhood beefnecks. Hate mail isn't their style.
Blue Moon!
Thank you, thank you so much!
Put the camera away. Now.
What's with the pictures?
I'll rephrase the question, and you rephrase the fuckin' answer. What're the pictures for? Hm?
entries.maleVariant: I'll rephrase the question, and you rephrase the fuckin' answer. What're the pictures for?

entries.femaleVariant: Uhhh, I don't know? For, like, eddies? To sell? That girl there's Blue Moon...? From Us Cracks...?
Put the camera away.
Noticed anything out of the ordinary?
Yeah, right! Blow me.
I tried being polite.
Mhm... Take pictures of her often?
entries.maleVariant: Huh... Take pictures of her often?

entries.femaleVariant: Yeah. Why? That against the law?
Anyone hang around her too much? Try to think.
And why would I spill that?
[Draw weapon]
Why are you following Blue Moon?
Nice nickname.
I heard you're following Blue Moon?
entries.maleVariant: I heard you're following Blue Moon.

entries.femaleVariant: Excuse me? This is the first I've seen her in person!
Nice nickname. Green Cloud.
What are you doing here?
That so? I just spoke with a still-taker who begs to differ. Has the shots to prove it, too.
Um... thanks.
"GC" for short. That's how you sign your letters, right?
Fuck...!
What're you up to?
Just taking a stroll... That not allowed?
Ah, sweet kid.
[Draw weapon]
Hilarious.
Because if some psycho decides to off Blue Moon, you won't have anyone to snap stills of.
Girl in green, over there. See her in every single frame. Funny, ain't it?
Mhm. Hilarious.
Not so close, V. Keep your distance.
You're getting too close, V!
Argh, whatever, this is pointless. I'm going home.
Just keep an eye on Blue Moon, hm?
I killed your stalker.
Your stalker's dead. Problem solved.
The fuck?! We had a deal, V! No killing!
Better him than you though, right?
This is a waste of time. Let's just call it a day, all right?
You're not taking this seriously, V. I'm going home.
OK. You can go.
When I call you, you'll start following me... But don't get too close, OK? We can't spook our guy.
Got it.
Phew... OK, here goes. Red Menace is keeping an extra lookout from a vantage point high up. Wish me luck!
Argh! OK, I'll handle this – make sure nobody spills to the media vultures. Bye, V. Thanks for your help, I guess...
I need a new faceplate, like, ASAP!
Why were you in a gun store?
What were you looking for in an iron depot?
What? What are you talking about? I wasn't in any store!
You're a shitty liar.
Dammit... no explosive rounds...
I'll just have to go with regular.
This alley's perfect for an ambush... Keep an eye out!
Phew... Another false alarm.
Look, we've been everywhere... Maybe he isn't here.
Let's just forget it, V. I'll tell Red Menace to pick us up.
Well... yeah, but...
Found our stalker. Stay where you are.
entries.maleVariant: Found your stalker. Stay where you are.

entries.femaleVariant: Oh, OK... Be careful. And remember, no killing! Please!
Let me know when the coast is clear.
OK... One last shot. If he doesn't show, we're calling it quits.
[Say nothing]
Keep your eyes peeled for anyone lurking around, watching me, spying on me from above... whatever. Anything creepy like that.
One less suspect to worry about...
Sure thing.
Hm-hm-hmmm... Just look natural, calm... Everything's OK...
Ooh, still haven't done a spread for them. What issue is this...?
Ugh, what what was that? Another weirdo like him and I'll hurl.
V, you there? Can't see you. Should be following me.
